                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>without you are <hi rend=\"underline\">asked—</hi><persName>Mr\n                                                  Block</persName> is in\n                                                  <placeName>Memphis</placeName><lb/>\n                                        <persName>Augustus</persName>, leaves tomorrow for\n                                                  <placeName>Quincy</placeName>, I wish you<lb/>\n                                        could marry them; I shall miss him greatly—<lb/> how is your\n                                        health? Aunty is as usual—<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Rosalie</persName>, remains in\n                                                  <placeName>Quincy</placeName>\n                                        <sic>untill</sic> after the wedding<lb/> when she\n                                                  <persName>Sarah</persName>,\n                                                  <persName>Eleanor</persName>, &amp; <persName>Anna\n                                                  Philipson</persName> &amp;c go to\n                                                  <placeName>New<lb/>\n                                                  =Orleans</placeName>—<persName>Rehine</persName>\n                                        is at the bay of <placeName>St Louis</placeName><lb/> with\n                                                  <persName>Sarah Levy</persName>—write me about\n                                        the<lb/> books—ever yours affectionately</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">\n                                                  <hi rend=\"underline\">A Block</hi>\n                                        </persName>\n                              </p>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3rn30q6t/canvas/p2"
